---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About — I am Shining"
  description="The story behind #Shining — a movement for people who show up with energy, optimism, and a golden glow."
  canonical="https://i-am-shining.com/about"
>
  <main id="main-content" tabindex="-1">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-inner">
        <h1>About <em>#Shining</em></h1>
      </div>
    </section>

    <article class="content">

      <section class="block">
        <h2>The movement</h2>
        <p>
          #Shining is for people who want to show up with energy, optimism, and a golden glow.
          It started as a simple idea: your profile picture is the first thing the world sees —
          why not make it radiant?
        </p>
        <p>
          The golden crescent frame is a signal. It says you are in your brightest season,
          that you choose to lead with warmth, and that you are not hiding your light.
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="divider"></div>

      <section class="block">
        <h2>How it started</h2>
        <p>
          Over a round of cold beers on a warm evening, a few friends got talking about how flat
          the feed had started to feel — everyone posting the same corporate headshots, the same
          polished smiles, none of the spark.
        </p>
        <p>
          The conversation went somewhere brighter: what if a profile picture could remind you
          to show up with a little more optimism? By the second pint there were sketches on a napkin.
          By the next morning there was code.
        </p>
        <p>
          Turns out an optimistic mindset is contagious — it spreads through every bling, every shine,
          every tiny golden pixel. That's how this began, and it's why we still keep it simple,
          playful, and free.
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="divider"></div>

      <section class="block">
        <h2>Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          Your photo never leaves your device. Everything — the canvas processing, the iridescent
          effect, the frame overlay — runs entirely in your browser. There are no uploads,
          no accounts, and no tracking.
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="divider"></div>

      <section class="block">
        <h2>Built by</h2>
        <p>
          Carl Hagerling — designer and developer based in Sweden.
          The source code is open on <a href="https://github.com/carlhagerling/i-am-shining" class="gold-link">GitHub</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="cta-block">
        <a href="/" class="cta-btn">Make your profile shine →</a>
      </div>

    </article>

    <footer class="site-footer">
      <p>#shining &mdash; keep it golden</p>
    </footer>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    padding-top: 5rem;
  }

  .hero {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 2.5rem 1rem 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 50%, hsla(40, 80%, 30%, 0.2) 0%, transparent 70%);
  }

  .hero-inner {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    line-height: 1.08;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
  }

  h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-gold-dim), var(--color-gold-light), var(--color-amber));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .content {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 640px;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem 4rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .block {
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin: 0 0 0.9rem;
  }

  p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .divider {
    width: 100%;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--color-gold-dim), transparent);
  }

  .gold-link {
    color: var(--color-gold-light);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  .cta-block {
    padding: 2.5rem 0 1rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .cta-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-gold-dim), var(--color-gold-light));
    color: #000;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .cta-btn:hover {
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .site-footer {
    padding: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
</style>
